Summary: Overview of methods and signals for detecting screen visibility in 3D space.

Method: bool is_on_screen() const
Returns true if the object is currently visible on the screen.

Signal: screen_entered()
Emitted when the VisibleOnScreenNotifier3D enters the screen.

Signal: screen_exited()
Emitted when the VisibleOnScreenNotifier3D exits the screen.
